# KeepItCool — design system

## Dove vive

- Token: [`app/globals.css`](app/globals.css) (`@theme inline` + `:root` gradients)
- Preview: [`app/styleguide/page.js`](app/styleguide/page.js) → `/styleguide`
- Note: [`app/content/design-handoff.js`](app/content/design-handoff.js)

Pattern come portfolio: `@source` esplicito, componenti in `app/components/`, copy in `app/content/`.

## Font

- Titoli: **Chillax Bold** → `font-display` / `font-chillax`
- Body/UI: **Outfit** → `font-body` / `font-outfit`

## Ink (gerarchia testo)

| Token | Hex | Uso |
|-------|-----|-----|
| `ink` | `#2c2c2c` | Testo principale, bordi nav-pill |
| `ink-muted` | `#434343` | Secondario, titoli sezione soft |
| `ink-warm` | `#503b14` | Testo su CTA giallo |

## Colori scoped — non usare fuori contesto

- **SDG** (`bg-sdg-*`): solo card Learning Goals
- **Game** (`game-card-talk/plan/play`): solo sezione TALK/PLAN/PLAY
- **Tag** (`tag-student`, `tag-psychologist`): solo pill label; nomi team = stile psychologist

## CTA vs highlight

- CTA: gradient radiale → classe `btn-cta` / `Button variant="cta"` — **non** `#fad724` flat
- Highlight testo: `highlight-yellow` (flat `#fad724` sotto parola)

## Utilities chiave

- `nav-pill`: crema 50% + `backdrop-blur`; `nav-pill-sticky` per sticky top
- `max-w-page`, `shadow-card`, tipografia fluida (`text-display`, `text-section`, …)

Gradient e classi scoped fuori `@layer` in `globals.css` (affidabilità Tailwind v4).
